

## 🔗 Working Links

### 1. Main Catalog (Text Format)
```
http://192.168.0.101:3000/
```
This shows the API homepage with all available endpoints listed in text format.

### 2. Menu JSON Data
```
http://192.168.0.101:3000/api/menu
```
This shows all menu items with:
- Names
- Prices
- Categories  
- Descriptions
- Image URLs
- Ratings
- Prep times

### 3. Test in Browser
Open these links in your browser to verify they work:
- First link should show the restaurant API welcome page
- Second link should show all 10 menu items with details

**Note:** Make sure your server is running (`node server.js`) before testing these links!
